title: Pup - Baby Seal (Original)
description: New born baby seals with yellow fur and blubber, weighed at around 11kg.

title: Pup - Baby Sea Otters
description: Baby sea otters can float on the water's surface, due to their dense and fluffy fur.

title: Pup - Baby Capybara
description: Baby capybara excellent swimmers, and can remain completely submerged for up to five minutes.

title: Chicks - Baby Penguin
description: Baby penguins are covered in soft, downy feathers and have a distinctive waddle.

title: Hoglets - Baby Hedgehog
description: Baby hedgehogs are covered in soft, white quills.

title: Cubs - Baby Panda
description: Baby pandas have a thick coat of black and white fur.
